episodes.title: Allegations of bodies buried at Epstein's New Mexico ranch prompt investigation calls
episodes.description:
New Mexico officials are urging an investigation into claims of bodies buried at Jeffrey Epstein's Zorro Ranch, following the release of documents related to the convicted sex offender's crimes.

KOAT Action 7 News is your home for New Mexico breaking news and weather. For your latest New Mexico news and weather visit: https://koat.com/
